txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the Orcs surrounding Gabilshathûr. Delivery of the items should be made to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
'Orcs using well-crafted sheaths... Only one thing possible there: they stole them! Get those back, and we'll put them to use.'
Thorin's Hall Task: Gilded Sword Sheaths
The dwarves at Gabilshathûr await a delivery of gilded sword sheaths to be made to Avar.
Deliver the gilded sword sheaths to Avar at Gabilshathûr in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver gilded sword sheaths from the Orcs surrounding Gabilshathûr to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the Orcs surrounding Gabilshathûr.
